              The new JEE avatar has given equal importance to board and entrance exams. Now board
              marks also plays an important and crucial role for admission to engineering colleges.
              The new format of JEE has created a more important need for coaching for students
              appearing for JEE examination apart from the regular 12th board. Now a days a lot of
              students spend their valuable time shuttling between their Home, Coaching Institutes
              and their Home. "TAKSHILA" under its TSPS Programme offers studies for students for
              boards and JEE together under one roof. This partnership ease the burden on students
              as they do not have to shuttle between the school and a coaching institute. Our aim is
              to help the students and give them in-depth knowledge of subjects. We believe that
              School is a best place for overall learning, we cannot substitute schools where
              students not only get the basics of academics but also get the lesson of life along
              with co-curricular activity, which we believe is the most important for every child.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-0">
              Takshila offers the tailor made solution for schools in which we maintain close
              co-ordination with school management. Our TSPS Programme not only aims JEE (main and
              Advance) or AIPMT (NEET), But we prepare students also for Olympiads, NTSE etc.
              Keeping school studies and student's performance in Boards at Top priority. Our team
              of teachers, who are well-versed with Board syllabus as well as IIT entrance exams,
              work in Shyncronised manner and the student learns the concepts in an ideal
              environment.
            </p>
